---
title: "Private Events & Parties | Nadine's Restaurant | Yorktown Heights, NY"
description: "Host your next private event, party, or special occasion at Nadine's Restaurant in Yorktown Heights, NY. Submit an inquiry to get started."
---

{% extends "layouts/base.njk" %}

{% block content %}
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden min-h-screen">
    {# Background image #}
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img src="{{ '/assets/images/slide_wine.jpg' | url }}" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-espresso/65"></div>
    </div>

    {# Content #}
    <div class="relative max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 flex justify-center">
      <div class="w-full lg:w-2/3 bg-cream rounded-2xl shadow-2xl p-10 fade-up">
        <p class="font-body font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-amber mb-3">Nadine's Restaurant</p>
        <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl text-espresso mb-4">Private Events</h1>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <span class="block w-12 h-px bg-amber/50"></span>
          <span class="text-amber">&#9670;</span>
          <span class="block w-12 h-px bg-amber/50"></span>
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-espresso/70 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Looking to host a private dinner, birthday celebration, corporate gathering, or special occasion? We'd love to make it memorable. Fill out the form below and a member of our team will be in touch to discuss how we can bring your event to life at Nadine's.
        </p>
        <iframe src="https://88restaurants.com/799/party_inquiry_forms" frameborder="0" width="100%" height="565" scrolling="no"></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
{% endblock %}
